caption.title: Data files used in the analyses in this paper in a zipped folder.
caption.p: AllGMRF_reduced.trees is the tree posterior for all 164 samples downsampled to 500 trees. MCC.tree is the maximum clade credibility tree for all 164 samples. PhyMLTreeFinal.tree is the ML tree of all 164 samples. dateswithuncertainty.txt contains the sampling date for each sample. ML, maximum likelihood.
